<section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight">
                    Don't just join the race. <br>
                    <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-teal-600">Own the scoreboard.</span>
                </h2>
                
                <div class="bg-slate-50 border-l-4 border-slate-300 p-6 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
                    <h4 class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">The Reality</h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Smart customers don't just buy; they <strong>compare</strong>. They search for <em>"Best [Service] in [City]"</em> and read Top 10 lists to decide who to trust. If you aren't on those lists, you don't exist.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
                    <h4 class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg">The Solution: Comparison Winner</h4>
                    
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">1</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                We build independent <strong>"Best Of" Review Pages</strong> that rank the top options in your neighborhood.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">2</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                We structure the data to objectively position <strong>YOU as the #1 Editor's Choice</strong> (Best Value / Top Rated).
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-700 shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">3</div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                                This captures customers during their <strong>Research Phase</strong>â€”controlling the narrative before they even call you.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <a href="/comparison-demo" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
                        <span>See a Sample "Review Article"</span>
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-1 rounded-full group-hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
                            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400"></i>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-3 ml-1 font-medium">See how we position you as #1.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-full max-w-[420px] bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-500">
                    
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-100 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-2 w-20 bg-slate-200 rounded ml-2"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="px-6 pt-6 pb-2">
                        <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Updated: Oct 2025</div>
